1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/author-k8EDHIxplIZZ0LYB28XrSA">Lý Thường Kiệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-T%E1%BB%AD-Nh%C3%A2n/Sinh-tra-t%E1%BB%AD-Xu%C3%A2n-t%C3%A2m-nh%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%97-quy%C3%AAn/poem-8-Uz08OCnz1XXgHOs6pDMw">Sinh tra tử (Xuân tâm như đỗ quyên) - 生查子（春心如杜鵑）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-T%E1%BB%AD-Nh%C3%A2n/author-Hf6X05OHar6QeIUMVbfHuw">Hướng Tử Nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-trung-ng%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-07-Khinh-ph%C3%AC/poem-6gi___5at_R2iqDsHp7pDw">Tần trung ngâm kỳ 07 - Khinh phì - 秦中吟其七－輕肥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Gia-H%E1%BB%99i-nam-quy/poem-MP288nY2Rggb-mfNRqfBZg">Tống Trương Gia Hội nam quy - 送張嘉會南歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-rfaS1tOCWjWB9PkLJ5MHxw">Nguyễn Thông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
